profile:
At Viking Sheds we are committed to building quality custom built sheds in Toronto (GTA). We design our products together with you to match your vision, needs and specifications.


What makes us unique from our competitors is that we will deliver a complete package starting with the sub-floor (cement or other) to the complete final structure of your vision.


We will work with you to select only quality and cost-effective materials.  We will cut no corners and will use sound building techniques that will guarantee a structurally solid final product. 



Your completed product will give your home the unique look that you are looking for. At Viking Sheds we offer the following products:

   -    Storage and Garden sheds
   -    Pavilions
   -    Pergolas
   -    Gazebos
   -    Cabanas
   -    Garden Greenhouses
